{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4fac8882f5","title":"右派言论——“今天居然大肆向文汇报开枪”","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选集》（天津：南开大学社会主义思想教育教研室，1957年9月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"98a6e676f1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":5,"articleId":"4fac8882f5"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"a8e36d72a2","name":"张步明"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b7095b2e18","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“今天居然大肆向文汇报开枪”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5"},{"id":"ce407a59c7","type":"authors","text":"南开大学张步明","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5"},{"id":"31cb19e4d2","type":"subtitle","text":"[张步明：南开大学中文系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5"},{"id":"57e39f15fe","type":"paragraph","text":"围剿更激烈了，今天居然大肆向文汇报开枪并且我班的一些小卒们还跟着呐喊。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5"},{"id":"96e6c10455","type":"paragraph","text":"我恨极了，我一点也不想同他们争论，我要守着普希金的诺言：“也不要与愚妄的人空作争论”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5"},{"id":"e27ffdb3e5","type":"paragraph","text":"“心灵是彻底的悲哀了，幻想完全消失，去他的吧，骗人的时代。”（摘自1957年7月5日日记）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5"},{"id":"90e3d56a31","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们要搞一个文艺复兴运动，办一个真正言论自由的刊物，只要是写不满现实反对三害的文章就可以在刊物上发表。……当前的主要任务是要找一些反教条主义和正直的人展开对党委会组织围剿（指的是当时的反右派斗争）的反击。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5"}],"page":{"id":"8cb2f90f4c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4fac8882f5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}